    <h1>Pre Run</h1>

      <p> The following exercises fall under dynamic stretches. This is the best way to warm up your cold muscles
        before intensive exertion.</p>

      <ul>
        <li>arm circles</li>
        <li>chair squats</li>
        <li>full 180 degree leg rotation and kick</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Watch this video to see the technique.</p>

      <video src="prestretch.mp4" width="400" height="800" controls></video>

      <p>We recommend the following reps per exercise. Feel free to adjust accordingly.</p>

      <div id="table_of_exercises">
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Exercise</th>
            <th>Number of Sets</th>
            <th>Number of Reps</th>
